sequenceDiagram
  title Sequence Flow: Manual Log Query Process
  participant U as Support Staff
  participant UI as Web UI
  participant API as Backend API
  participant DB as SQL Server

  U->>UI: Submit log query
  UI->>API: Send query parameters
  API->>DB: Fetch logs
  DB-->>API: Return log data
  API-->>UI: Return log data
  UI-->>U: Display log table